Yet this is but poſitive all the while; She aſcends a degree higher. And ſo it was, as oft as he paſsed by, he turned in thither to eat bread. — She was not weary of welldoing; but, like the Sun, rejoyed to Run her courſe. She was none of thoſe, that give a bit, and a knock: and ſhe Scorned to return that Common, and penurious Objection, You were here once before. Grace is Communicative, and, like the Widon's Oil, never ſtops ſo long, as there is a veſſel more to receive it. Perſeverance in Goodneſs makes a Chriſtian compleat. You did run well, who did hinder you; Gal. v. 7. Many for a Spirt run Swiftly, their Setting cut is Violent, but that's not perpetual, like Jades, they are ſoon tired, the Chariot-wheels of their Devotion are taken off, that, at laſt, they drive heavily, One jeeringly ſaid to Hannibal;
Hannibal, Vincere ſcis, Hannibal, uti Victoria neſcis. to get the Victory thou know'ſt full well,
But after how to uſe't, thou can'ſt not tell.
